release_note: Made it compatible to iOS 14.2 Some users reported a recording issue which has been corrected

There have been a many requests to shorten some songs to reduce a song s intro closing and all interludes leaving only the stanzas with the lyrics. This feature has now been added and is accessible in settings or on the play screen. Many duet songs now offer an accompanying female male part of a duet sung by a singer enabling you to sing a duet without a partner. We have added an account less demo mode for you to explore the features of our app without registering with your email address. We have fixed many bugs and made many improvements in the user interface: and improvements in search for songs.

UI improvements added player which can adjust the pitch and tempo of the track and the settings can be saved for future use. MeraGana Karaoke has the largest library of Indian Karaoke in the World and permits unlimited use on any device. The new feature of pitch and tempo enhances your experience by permitting you to adjust the music to your level of comfort and then saving the setting. So when you play the song on any device the song is played using the settings that you saved.
